---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About Us | Luna Handyman Solutions">
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-neutral-white via-neutral-light to-white">
    <div class="absolute -left-24 top-6 h-64 w-64 rounded-full bg-primary/10 blur-3xl"></div>
    <div class="absolute right-0 bottom-6 h-60 w-60 rounded-full bg-accent/20 blur-3xl"></div>

    <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 md:py-20 grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-[1.15fr,0.85fr] items-center">
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-primary font-semibold">About Luna</p>
        <h1 class="display-font text-4xl md:text-5xl font-semibold text-secondary leading-[1.05]">
          Builders who keep projects calm, clear, and on schedule.
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-neutral-dark-gray leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">
          We’re a Bay Area team that treats every home or workspace like our own—protecting your space, coordinating every trade, and keeping you updated without the runaround.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-neutral-light px-3 py-1 text-sm text-neutral-dark"><span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-primary"></span>Licensed + insured</span>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-neutral-light px-3 py-1 text-sm text-neutral-dark"><span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-primary"></span>Occupied-space specialists</span>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-neutral-light px-3 py-1 text-sm text-neutral-dark"><span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-primary"></span>Transparent pricing</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border border-neutral-light-gray rounded-3xl shadow-lg p-6 space-y-4">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
          <div>
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-primary">Operating since</p>
            <p class="display-font text-2xl font-semibold text-secondary">2008</p>
          </div>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-accent text-neutral-dark px-3 py-1 text-sm font-semibold">15+ years on site</span>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-3 text-center">
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-light-gray bg-neutral-light px-3 py-4 shadow-sm">
            <p class="display-font text-xl font-semibold text-secondary">100+</p>
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-mid">Projects</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-light-gray bg-neutral-light px-3 py-4 shadow-sm">
            <p class="display-font text-xl font-semibold text-secondary">4.9★</p>
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-mid">Client rating</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-light-gray bg-neutral-light px-3 py-4 shadow-sm">
            <p class="display-font text-xl font-semibold text-secondary">72 hrs</p>
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-mid">Site visit window</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-dark-gray">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-primary"></span><span>Dedicated lead on every job with daily check-ins.</span></li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-primary"></span><span>Structural, MEP, finishes, and closeout handled in-house.</span></li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-primary"></span><span>Clean protection for occupied spaces—dust control, ventilation, and tidy staging.</span></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <main class="space-y-20 md:space-y-24">
    <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 grid md:grid-cols-[1.05fr,0.95fr] gap-10 items-start">
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-primary font-semibold">Mission</p>
        <h2 class="display-font text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold text-secondary leading-tight">Clarity first, then craftsmanship.</h2>
        <p class="text-neutral-dark-gray text-lg leading-relaxed">
          We combine straightforward communication with disciplined schedules and finish-grade work. You always know what’s happening on site, why decisions are made, and when you’ll see the next milestone.
        </p>
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-light-gray bg-white p-4 shadow-sm">
            <p class="font-semibold text-secondary">Everyday clarity</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-neutral-dark-gray">Daily photo logs, budget visibility, and change-order transparency.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-light-gray bg-white p-4 shadow-sm">
            <p class="font-semibold text-secondary">Craftsmanship first</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-neutral-dark-gray">Vetted trades, tight tolerances, and a finish that feels intentional.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-light-gray bg-white p-4 shadow-sm">
            <p class="font-semibold text-secondary">Risk handled</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-neutral-dark-gray">Permits, inspections, and safety protocols planned before demo.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-light-gray bg-white p-4 shadow-sm">
            <p class="font-semibold text-secondary">Aftercare</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-neutral-dark-gray">Punch completion, warranties, and maintenance guidance.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-3xl bg-secondary text-neutral-light p-7 shadow-xl border border-secondary-dark/40 space-y-5">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
          <div>
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-accent">From the lead</p>
            <p class="display-font text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-white">Why we work the way we do</p>
          </div>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-neutral-white/10 px-3 py-1 text-sm text-neutral-white">Hands-on crews</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-neutral-light-gray text-lg leading-relaxed">
          “Clients trust us because we keep things calm: tight protection, tidy sites, and updates you can act on. Our crews stay on the same schedule, so the work moves without surprises.”
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-neutral-white/10 px-3 py-1 text-sm"><span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent"></span>Daily photo logs</span>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-neutral-white/10 px-3 py-1 text-sm"><span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent"></span>Jobsite protection</span>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-neutral-white/10 px-3 py-1 text-sm"><span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent"></span>Milestone QA</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-neutral-light-gray py-16 px-6">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto space-y-8">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between gap-4">
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-primary font-semibold">How we work</p>
            <h3 class="display-font text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold text-secondary leading-tight">A simple four-step rhythm.</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-dark-gray text-lg max-w-2xl">Clear milestones keep momentum: map the scope, plan and permit, build with updates, and close out fast.</p>
          </div>
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-primary text-neutral-white font-semibold px-5 py-3 rounded-xl shadow-md hover:bg-primary-dark transition"
          >
            Book a walkthrough
            <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-5 shadow-sm border border-neutral-light-gray">
            <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-primary font-semibold">01</p>
            <p class="display-font text-lg font-semibold text-secondary mt-1 mb-2">Scope & site walk</p>
            <p class="text-neutral-dark-gray text-sm leading-relaxed">Document conditions, risks, and quick wins; align budget targets and constraints.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-5 shadow-sm border border-neutral-light-gray">
            <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-primary font-semibold">02</p>
            <p class="display-font text-lg font-semibold text-secondary mt-1 mb-2">Plan & permit</p>
            <p class="text-neutral-dark-gray text-sm leading-relaxed">Build plan, schedule, and procurement mapped; permitting and inspections handled.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-5 shadow-sm border border-neutral-light-gray">
            <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-primary font-semibold">03</p>
            <p class="display-font text-lg font-semibold text-secondary mt-1 mb-2">Build + update</p>
            <p class="text-neutral-dark-gray text-sm leading-relaxed">Coordinated trades, daily logs, and clean protection for occupied spaces.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-5 shadow-sm border border-neutral-light-gray">
            <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-primary font-semibold">04</p>
            <p class="display-font text-lg font-semibold text-secondary mt-1 mb-2">QC & handoff</p>
            <p class="text-neutral-dark-gray text-sm leading-relaxed">Punch resolved quickly, warranties issued, and post-build support if you need it.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
